Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.99,0:00:04.24,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,呂布軍對陣劉備曹操聯軍
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.60,0:00:08.41,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,呂布軍武將張遼驍勇善戰
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.41,0:00:13.50,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,令關羽大為欽佩 遂求曹操饒他一命
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.86,0:00:15.07,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,數年後
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.39,0:00:19.31,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,被曹操軍逼入絕境的關羽拒絕投降
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.31,0:00:21.43,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,想自尋了斷
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.74,0:00:25.07,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,不過 張遼拚死說服了他
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.59,0:00:29.35,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,相傳二人後來仍維繫著友誼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.96,0:00:31.11,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,時間來到現代
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.11,0:00:35.19,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,此處也有兩個人即將結下深厚的友誼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.62,0:00:37.41,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,英子與七海進行街頭演出
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.41,0:00:39.58,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,想藉此找到自我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.88,0:00:43.23,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我也想跟七海一樣 唱出自己的風格
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.60,0:00:46.48,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,二人在演出之外也一起行動
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.48,0:00:48.96,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,漸漸對彼此敞開了心扉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.96,0:00:51.88,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,真希望我們在一起時能一直面帶笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.88,0:00:55.54,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,像想七海一樣 拓展表現力
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.99,0:00:57.42,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,產生了這個想法的英子
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.42,0:00:59.28,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,竭盡全力 不停唱歌
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.60,0:01:02.43,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,英子 剛才那次唱得非常好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.78,0:01:05.45,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,終於找到自我的英子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.45,0:01:07.06,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,隨即前去找Kid
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.67,0:01:10.42,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,二人萌生的深厚友誼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.42,0:01:12.59,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,今後仍將持續下去
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.98,0:01:14.26,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,看似如此
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.31,0:01:25.14,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,CHANCE×CHANCE
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.14,0:01:26.98,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,逢！！Chitty Chitty Bang Bang
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.98,0:01:28.86,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,哀！？Chitty Chitty CHANCE CHANCE
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.86,0:01:30.76,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,嗚呼！Chitty Chitty Bang Bang
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.76,0:01:32.59,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,愛！！Choki Choki Bang Bang
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.59,0:01:34.43,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,HIGH Chitty Chitty Bang Bang
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.43,0:01:36.29,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,哀！？Chitty Chitty CHANCE CHANCE
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.29,0:01:38.18,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,嗚呼！Chitty Chitty Bang Bang
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.18,0:01:38.98,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,愛！！Choki Choki Bang Bang
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.98,0:01:42.06,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,無論張三李四
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.12,0:01:46.37,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,全都心血來潮 好難受
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.37,0:01:49.53,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,龍舌蘭喝到醉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.92,0:01:53.64,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,不存在的妄想連連 閃耀
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.64,0:01:58.11,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,夢是潘多拉 讓人想要打開
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.11,0:02:01.18,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,大家都期待著派對咖
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.18,0:02:05.59,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,今晚不知道 爬不爬富士山
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.59,0:02:08.84,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,決戰是週末的宿命
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.34,0:02:10.12,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,CHANCE×CHANCE
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.12,0:02:12.09,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,逢！！Chitty Chitty Bang Bang
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.37,0:02:16.81,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,別裝模作樣 好好享受 今晚嗨起來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.81,0:02:17.56,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,CHANCE×CHANCE
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.56,0:02:19.59,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,哀！？Chitty Chitty Bang Bang
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.87,0:02:24.37,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,無論再鬱悶 今晚也要一起派對
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.37,0:02:25.12,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,CHANCE×CHANCE
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.12,0:02:27.13,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,嗚呼！Chitty Chitty Bang Bang
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.43,0:02:31.81,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,愚蠢的人更該HIGH 完美社會
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.81,0:02:32.59,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,CHANCE×CHANCE
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.59,0:02:34.55,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,愛！！Choki Choki Bang Bang
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.87,0:02:39.52,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,大家都是明日的超級明星 今晚一起派對
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.47,0:02:55.44,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.31,0:02:57.16,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,久遠
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.53,0:03:01.28,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,聽說你最近在街頭唱歌啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.28,0:03:02.28,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,你怎麼知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.28,0:03:03.97,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我想你應該很清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.40,0:03:05.94,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,立刻停止這種行為
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.15,0:03:10.53,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,另外 好像有人跟你一起唱歌
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.83,0:03:13.33,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,你必須跟那種人一刀兩斷
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.59,0:03:17.81,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,在會議開始前趕回來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.16,0:03:19.09,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,明白了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.19,0:03:27.69,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,（為了蒼生）
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.69,0:03:31.93,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,（Cause you gave me whispers of love all night）
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.93,0:03:33.06,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,哦？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.19,0:03:37.19,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.31,0:03:39.16,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.08,0:03:42.34,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,但是還不夠
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.24,0:03:45.21,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,雖然比之前好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.21,0:03:47.15,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,但是缺乏自我的本質
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.69,0:03:51.72,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,為什麼而唱歌 必須表現出來才行
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.21,0:03:57.16,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.22,0:04:02.83,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,說是必須表現出為什麼而唱歌才行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.59,0:04:06.65,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我實在想不到該怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.25,0:04:11.68,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,你唱出本色了的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.08,0:04:17.29,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,你要相信我 別信那布丁老頭
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.83,0:04:19.79,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.12,0:04:23.93,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,對了 找個地方散散心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.20,0:04:25.38,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,散心？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.85,0:04:28.05,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,孔明給我的袋子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.85,0:04:33.24,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,SKY SQUARE展望台門票？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.99,0:04:37.49,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,單是這樣浪費實在
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.49,0:04:39.19,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,想要突破下個障礙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.19,0:04:42.02,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,想強化技能 這不是消化比賽
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.02,0:04:43.87,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我們集結起來 唱響天籟
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.87,0:04:45.06,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,耶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.38,0:04:47.17,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,真的太感謝大家了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.17,0:04:49.44,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,真沒想到能來這麼多人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.44,0:04:51.01,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,肯定會來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.01,0:04:54.94,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,老家的英雄又要跟赤兔馬對決了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.94,0:04:56.29,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,當然想幫你了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.29,0:04:59.06,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,只要你不嫌棄我們 每天都可以陪你練
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.06,0:05:00.49,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,是吧 佐佐仔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.49,0:05:01.14,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.27,0:05:05.62,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,畢竟每天這個點正好剛下班 沒什麼開心事可幹
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.62,0:05:07.80,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,這樣啊 真辛苦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.75,0:05:09.86,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.14,0:05:12.49,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,剛下班 沒開心事可幹
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.49,0:05:14.36,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,佐佐仔 你剛才押韻了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.63,0:05:18.50,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,因為你上次說我根本沒押韻嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.10,0:05:21.68,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,不動聲色 下戰書
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.68,0:05:23.35,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,讓人驚愕 高性能
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.83,0:05:25.51,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,馬上就還回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.51,0:05:27.99,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,佐佐仔 竟敢挑戰KABE太人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.99,0:05:29.56,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,你太狂了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.08,0:05:31.01,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.01,0:05:33.79,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,練五年再說了 我要上廁所 走了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.79,0:05:35.56,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,好厲害 押韻了三句
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.04,0:05:38.48,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,不過 你這押韻也太爛了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.48,0:05:41.19,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,說什麼呢 這才是我的風格啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.36,0:05:43.41,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,有心事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.12,0:05:45.00,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.00,0:05:48.93,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,-這才是我的風格嗎 -沒有 擔心沒有 我的頻道人氣沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.42,0:05:52.62,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,什麼破東西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.62,0:05:57.87,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,哇 好高
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.87,0:06:00.37,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,這太激動人心了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.01,0:06:02.35,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,飛艇耶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.62,0:06:09.43,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,話說 七海唱歌時有想法嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.43,0:06:11.08,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,比如想為什麼而唱歌
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.41,0:06:12.31,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.92,0:06:16.37,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我什麼都沒想吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.66,0:06:18.06,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我唱歌只是因為喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.63,0:06:19.79,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,在街頭是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.31,0:06:21.81,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,在街頭是這樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.68,0:06:24.31,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我早就在想了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.31,0:06:26.31,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,你肯定是職業歌手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.31,0:06:27.72,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,唱得太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.37,0:06:30.30,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,算是職業歌手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.30,0:06:31.82,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,雖然沒露臉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.82,0:06:33.14,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我就知道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.14,0:06:34.94,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,有種職業人的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.27,0:06:36.69,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,是簽約歌手嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.23,0:06:39.43,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,還是著名的巡演歌手？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.37,0:06:47.75,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我覺得還是得告訴你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.87,0:06:51.61,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,因為這可能是最後一次了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.93,0:06:53.97,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,你說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.81,0:07:01.44,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,對不起 我本該早點說出來的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.87,0:07:04.97,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,但我想對你以真面目相待
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.88,0:07:09.14,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,請看
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.58,0:07:12.37,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我是偶像樂隊AZALEA的貝斯手兼主唱
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.16,0:07:15.14,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,久遠七海
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.49,0:07:18.43,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.25,0:07:21.32,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,不是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.74,0:07:27.44,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,派對咖孔明
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.93,0:07:32.63,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,七海是AZALEA的成員？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.91,0:07:36.07,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,不是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.50,0:07:39.29,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,給人的感覺差得也太遠了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.24,0:07:45.00,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,起初不是這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.57,0:07:51.51,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,雙葉打的鼓太完美了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.51,0:07:52.69,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,謝謝誇獎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.69,0:07:54.54,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,一夏也彈得非常棒哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.54,0:07:56.32,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,喂 那我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.32,0:07:59.98,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,還用說嗎 七海的歌聲和貝斯才是中堅力量
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.61,0:08:03.50,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,好期待文化節啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.81,0:08:06.37,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我還沒當眾演奏過
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.37,0:08:08.01,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,還是有點擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.01,0:08:09.76,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,大家都一樣啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.76,0:08:11.02,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,放心好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.31,0:08:13.45,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,嗯 也是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.25,0:08:15.18,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.18,0:08:17.12,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,說起來還沒定呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.12,0:08:18.61,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我們的樂隊名
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.61,0:08:19.81,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,真的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.81,0:08:22.64,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,練習太投入 這麼重要的事都忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.64,0:08:26.18,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,那麼 大家一人想一個名字吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.12,0:08:29.27,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,那就你先想一個吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.61,0:08:30.57,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.85,0:08:34.28,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我覺得叫「樂隊樂隊樂隊」挺好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.28,0:08:34.95,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,駁回
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.86,0:08:38.24,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,為什麼是樂隊樂隊樂隊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.24,0:08:40.83,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,因為是三個人 所以叫樂隊樂隊樂隊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.12,0:08:43.53,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我來 可以說我想的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.89,0:08:46.08,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,七海 一夏 雙葉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.08,0:08:47.91,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,從三個名字中各取一個字
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.91,0:08:49.04,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,就叫七一葉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.30,0:08:50.42,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,這名字怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.16,0:08:52.53,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,還不錯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.53,0:08:53.51,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.51,0:08:55.58,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,雙葉呢 有主意嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.58,0:08:59.50,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,嗯 我想過一個名字
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.80,0:09:02.88,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,叫AZALEA怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.52,0:09:07.80,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,AZALEA？什麼意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.45,0:09:10.80,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,是花的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.62,0:09:14.14,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,然後這種花的花語是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.45,0:09:15.97,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,青春的喜悅
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.40,0:09:18.61,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,不錯嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.07,0:09:21.33,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我跟高中的朋友組了樂隊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.65,0:09:24.05,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,一起追求自己想要的音樂
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.37,0:09:26.40,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,很棒 相當棒
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.87,0:09:30.22,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,出道演唱會是文化節演出
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.89,0:09:35.05,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.05,0:09:36.51,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,很帥哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.05,0:09:40.97,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,不得了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.53,0:09:45.73,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,真的太爽了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.50,0:09:47.91,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,到現在還有雞皮疙瘩
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.91,0:09:50.33,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,是啊 太感動了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.55,0:09:57.37,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我無論是在高中 還是畢業之後
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.37,0:09:59.09,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,都要一直玩音樂
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.39,0:10:02.38,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,所以 你們也一起來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.72,0:10:05.94,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,喂喂 我們才高一哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.94,0:10:08.98,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,那麼遙遠的事 誰說得准啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.27,0:10:12.23,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,說什麼啦 你們不想玩音樂嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.21,0:10:17.38,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,當然想啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.33,0:10:22.15,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,好 AZALEA要起步了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.28,0:10:24.79,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我說你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.79,0:10:29.14,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,後來 我們的高中生活就是以音樂為中心了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.61,0:10:31.10,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,畢業之後也一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.35,0:10:34.59,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我們三個為了繼續玩音樂 來到了東京
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.51,0:10:36.90,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,原來是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.90,0:10:39.09,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,雖說來到東京了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.09,0:10:41.63,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,但一直沒遇到機會
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.22,0:10:44.77,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,辦演唱會也吸引不到觀眾
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.50,0:10:49.36,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,但那時還算開心的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.70,0:10:53.39,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,因為我們能堅持玩最喜歡的音樂
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.72,0:10:54.60,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,還算開心？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.67,0:11:00.41,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,直到那傢伙出現
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.80,0:11:07.57,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,那麼 你們想玩怎樣的音樂呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.97,0:11:09.78,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,當然是搖滾
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.08,0:11:12.52,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,能震撼聽眾心靈的那種
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.52,0:11:16.29,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,沒錯 畢竟我們一直在玩有激情的音樂
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.29,0:11:18.24,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,而且AZALEA這名字
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.24,0:11:21.37,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,源於青春的喜悅這個花語
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.37,0:11:22.62,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,所以 我們還是希望
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.62,0:11:26.89,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,繼續表達剛組建樂隊時的激動心情
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.89,0:11:29.40,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,哦 雙葉 說得真好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.09,0:11:31.04,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,無聊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.15,0:11:34.24,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,你們果然什麼都不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.47,0:11:37.01,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,組建樂隊已有三年
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.41,0:11:41.38,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,可容納50人的會場 實際到場的觀眾卻連一半都不到
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.51,0:11:46.94,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,這種默默無聞的樂隊 趕緊解散吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.98,0:11:49.83,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,你憑什麼這樣說我們
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.83,0:11:51.21,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,聽我把話說完
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.79,0:11:53.77,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我是要給你們機會
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.77,0:11:54.63,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,機會？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.75,0:11:57.58,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,只要你們唱我的歌
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.58,0:12:00.53,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我保證兩年之內 你們能在體育場開演唱會
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.91,0:12:02.09,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,體育場？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.09,0:12:03.69,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,兩年之內？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.69,0:12:06.15,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,如果你們錯過這次機會
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.45,0:12:08.82,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,你們這輩子都會默默無聞
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.29,0:12:11.94,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,你說什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.17,0:12:14.89,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,開什麼玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.73,0:12:18.90,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,玉不琢不成器
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.40,0:12:28.54,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,好好考慮一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.32,0:12:34.37,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,是他請我們來 結果跩成這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.37,0:12:36.71,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,誰要唱你的歌啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.71,0:12:39.02,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我也討厭他的歌
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.60,0:12:40.27,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.97,0:12:45.11,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,唐澤包裝的作品 都很紅吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.64,0:12:47.58,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,機會一定會來的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.58,0:12:48.55,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,沒錯 沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.55,0:12:50.50,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,就靠我們的方式努力下去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.85,0:12:52.05,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,就是說嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.71,0:12:57.27,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我們原本對自己的音樂很自信
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.12,0:12:59.00,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.90,0:13:01.64,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我們並不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.73,0:13:04.01,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,該怎樣才能紅起來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.02,0:13:07.74,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,票沒賣完啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.09,0:13:09.60,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,又得自己掏錢了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.52,0:13:12.33,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,得多打點工了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.33,0:13:15.25,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,光是住在東京就得花不少錢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.25,0:13:17.71,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我可不要回老家
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.71,0:13:19.71,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,（兼職招聘訊息綜合網站）
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.21,0:13:29.46,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,當時的生活很緊張
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.03,0:13:33.80,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我該去打工了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.80,0:13:35.26,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.97,0:13:37.85,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.61,0:13:45.40,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,喂 我是AZALEA的久遠七海
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.24,0:13:50.11,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,之前太狂妄了 真是萬分抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.70,0:13:52.87,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,請包裝我們吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.38,0:13:54.39,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,這樣就好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.49,0:13:57.80,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我以前也曾誤會過
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.78,0:14:01.49,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,誤以為做想做的事就能活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.03,0:14:05.94,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,然而 只有取悅別人才能收到報酬
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.37,0:14:09.08,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我當時並不明白這理所當然的道理
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.92,0:14:11.19,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,不必擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.76,0:14:14.37,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我一定會把你們捧紅的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.71,0:14:17.07,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,是 那就麻煩您了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.77,0:14:27.17,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,這服裝是什麼情況
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.76,0:14:29.62,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,那是AZALEA的服裝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.30,0:14:32.82,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,從今天起 你們要穿上這服裝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.61,0:14:35.63,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,不行 不行 這太扯了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.63,0:14:36.75,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,是吧 七海
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.32,0:14:39.32,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,七海？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.77,0:14:41.29,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,絕對能紅
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.78,0:14:43.87,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,服裝 歌曲 編舞
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.87,0:14:45.90,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,全部要聽從我們的指示
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.49,0:14:47.69,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,既然想紅
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.32,0:14:49.23,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,就穿上
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.26,0:14:51.39,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,真的假的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.99,0:14:54.87,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,這也是你們的服裝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.37,0:14:59.65,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,從今天起 你們將重生為全新的AZALEA
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.98,0:15:02.14,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,七海 怎麼辦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.04,0:15:05.54,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,這樣就能紅對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.12,0:15:08.44,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,對 絕對能紅
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.10,0:15:13.86,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,換身服裝而已 怎麼能改變我們
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.28,0:15:17.15,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,現在就忍著穿上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.95,0:15:19.02,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,真的假的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.19,0:15:21.79,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,既然七海都這麼說了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.65,0:15:25.19,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,唐澤說的沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.62,0:15:27.07,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,粉絲馬上就變多了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.75,0:15:29.38,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我們是AZALEA
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.51,0:15:38.74,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,等一下 怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.13,0:15:40.00,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,也就是說
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.26,0:15:43.41,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,下次的演奏可以不用親自彈
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.87,0:15:46.02,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,相對的 你們要專注於表演
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.37,0:15:48.34,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,這才是客人想要的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.34,0:15:49.62,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.62,0:15:51.87,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我們是樂隊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.62,0:15:56.45,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,後來 唐澤說什麼我們都照辦了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.22,0:15:58.28,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,結果就是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.84,0:16:05.22,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,粉絲激增
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.75,0:16:07.48,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,CD和周邊也大賣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.94,0:16:11.32,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我們能只靠音樂活下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.50,0:16:15.36,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,只不過
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.80,0:16:17.62,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,這個月的進賬你看了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.62,0:16:20.90,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,看了 我給家裡買了台洗碗機
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.90,0:16:23.44,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,那個 剛才的演唱會…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.59,0:16:25.47,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.66,0:16:36.05,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,對了 我也買了台新微波爐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.05,0:16:37.28,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.28,0:16:40.84,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,挺好啊 我要不要也換新的家電呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.80,0:16:42.48,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.83,0:16:44.51,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,七海 你這就要回去了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.89,0:16:47.89,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,嗯 我去唱幾首歌散散心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.20,0:16:49.29,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.25,0:16:58.50,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,只是服裝就改變了我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.62,0:17:00.77,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,但是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.77,0:17:03.13,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,跟你一起唱過歌后 我就明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.90,0:17:07.25,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我不想唱唐澤的歌了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.83,0:17:11.49,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,但是 AZALEA早就不只屬於我們了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.81,0:17:14.30,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,已經是一個團隊 投入了大量的資金
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.73,0:17:16.76,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我也不想背叛想捧紅我們的工作人員
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.76,0:17:18.96,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,以及來看我們演出的粉絲
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.50,0:17:22.63,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,對不起 一直瞞著你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.64,0:17:29.15,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我也必須告訴你一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.45,0:17:35.49,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,關係到能否出席SUMMER SONIA的10萬讚企劃
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.11,0:17:37.84,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我也參加了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.90,0:17:42.14,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.47,0:17:44.50,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,畢竟你唱得這麼好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.29,0:17:54.31,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,七海
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.74,0:17:56.89,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,原來心裡藏著這樣的煩惱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.81,0:18:00.00,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我根本沒發現
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.73,0:18:03.57,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我就只想著自己 單方面收穫著勇氣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.38,0:18:06.24,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,既然如此
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.50,0:18:09.25,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.35,0:18:11.53,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我要唱歌
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.11,0:18:13.27,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,在這唱嗎
